nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "드립", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "하지", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "무엇", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "꺼뜨리지", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "로운", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "때문", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "만큼", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "사들", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "사사", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "이러", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "자분", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "^수사가", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "^최순실씨가", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "^최순실씨로부터", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "^사람들", replacement ="", nouns2)
nouns2 <- gsub(pattern = "^대통령의", replacement ="", nouns2)

nouns2 = nouns2[nchar(nouns2) >= 2]
wordcount = table(nouns2)  # 단어 빈도 계산   
wc = sort(wordcount, decreasing = T)

pal <- brewer.pal(6, "Dark2")
windowsFonts(malgun=windowsFont("맑은 고딕"))
wordcloud(words=names(wc), freq=wc, colors=pal, min.freq=1, scale = c(4, 0.5), 
          random.order=F, family="malgun")

3 문제 2

iris data를 다음과 같은 방법으로 train 데이터와 test 데이터로 나누시오.

nn = nrow(iris)
tr = sort(sample(x = 1:nn, size = nn*0.8, replace = F))
train = iris[tr, ]
test = iris[-tr, ]

# 회귀분석에서 p값이 유의수준을 초과해 귀무가설이 채택되는 변수들을 제거
pidmodel=glm(diabetes~pregnant+glucose+pressure+mass+pedigree,data = PIDtrain,family = binomial(link = "logit"))

PIDtest$predict=predict(pidmodel,newdata = PIDtest,type = "response")
PIDtest$pred=ifelse(PIDtest$predict>=0.5,"pos","neg")
# 50% 이상은 pos, 50% 미만은 neg
PIDtest$pred=factor(PIDtest$pred)

confusionMatrix(PIDtest$pred,reference=PIDtest$diabetes)
